Privacy Policy
All apps by MocaFactory is not responsible for the contents of the pictures, images, logos, drawings, and any other visual media that its users use with the software.
Our apps do not collect or use any personal information from their users.
The only personal information from the user accessible to MocaDeco, MocaBanner, Picolla, Recolla, Retrograf, Neongraf, Antiqgraf, Infragraf, Pastelgraf, DonutsPop and VVD is if the user makes contact through the contact button placed in the ABOUT section of the app, or by typing directly the email address
support@mocadeco.com
, which will allow MocaDeco, MocaBanner, Picolla, Recolla, Retrograf, Neongraf, Antiqgraf, Infragraf, Pastelgraf, DonutsPop and VVD to respond back to the user’s email address.
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time for any reason. We will notify you of any changes to our Privacy Policy by posting the new Privacy Policy at
http://www.mocadeco.com/privacy
.
In case personal information is needed, MocaDeco, MocaBanner, Picolla, Recolla, Retrograf, Neongraf, Antiqgraf, Infragraf, Pastelgraf, DonutsPop and VVD will identify the purposes for which information is being collected.
We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy from time to time without notice. Please review the Privacy Policy from time to time so that you will be apprised of any changes. These changes are effective immediately after they are posted on this page.